Spectrum HHI  HHI is a division of Spectrum Brands Holdings, Inc. (NYSE: SPB). Spectrum Brands is a global, diversified consumer products company and a leading supplier of consumer batteries, residential locksets, residential builders’ hardware and faucets, shaving and grooming products, personal care products, small household appliances, specialty pet supplies, lawn and garden and home pest control products, and personal insect repellents.   Visit SpectrumBrands.com »




Kwikset  Kwikset manufactures and markets a complete line of door locks and door hardware including door knobs, door levers, deadbolts, handlesets, pocket door hardware and electronic keyless entry locks for residential and light commercial applications.  Visit Kwikset.com »




Weiser  Weiser is a recognized leader in innovation and product development providing high quality Fashion Doorware™ and offering a variety of solutions for both consumers and dealers.  Visit WeiserLock.com »




Pfister  For over a century, Pfister has been a leader in the plumbing industry, creating stylish, innovative, dependable kitchen and bath faucets and accessories that are often industry firsts. Visit PfisterFaucets.com »




Stanley  Stanley is a global organization supplying hardware and tools for the architectural, consumer, industrial and residential markets worldwide. Utilizing state-of-the-art research, manufacturing and quality-control capabilities that incorporate the latest techniques, procedures and equipment, Stanley continues to deliver the innovative, high quality products that have made the Stanley name synonymous with the highest craftsmanship and dependability for more than 150 years.  Visit StanleyHardware.com »




National Hardware  In 1901 National Manufacturing started out as a small wagon company in Sterling, Illinois. Soon after the focus switched to hardware manufacturing and sales. Today, National has grown into an international force, dedicated to creating the best hardware options for our valued customers.  Visit Natman.com »




Baldwin  Baldwin delivers timeless beauty in handcrafted products in contemporary, rustic and traditional styles. So no matter what your design aesthetic, you will never compromise on style or quality.  Visit BaldwinHardware.com »




Fanal  FANAL® has more than 60 years of history in the market as one of Mexico’s leading brands. Our product offering includes a wide variety of locks, hinges, padlocks and other home hardware products. Our products are manufactured in Mexico, by Mexican craftsmen, and are imported from different countries around the world.  Visit Fanal.com.mx »




EZSET  As one of the world’s leading lock manufacturers, Tong Lung proudly offers EZSET’s® world-class security and design to 15 million families. For over 30 years, EZSET® has provided customers with high quality products and professional service through continuous innovation and industry experience.  Visit EZSET.com.tw »




Tell
 Tell is focused on selling commercial doors and hardware. Our product lines consist of commercial and residential grade door locksets, builder hardware, door closers, exit devices, hinges, thresholds, weather stripping, trim, auxiliary hardware and commercial steel doors and frames.
Visit Tellmfg.com »












































































 ONE TEAM DELIVERING A GREAT CUSTOMER EXPERIENCE 
Spectrum Brands hires, develops, and rewards great people who understand the importance of a strong culture that values integrity, commitment, teamwork, and diversity. Our employees have a passion for developing great products and innovative solutions that meet our customers’ needs.  By satisfying customers, we improve people’s lives, and by doing so, create value for our stockholders – providing a great future for our customers, our company, and our employees.  Explore our Career Center for information about joining the Spectrum Brands HHI team. CAREER CENTER »     


 SUPPLIER PORTAL For our current and potential supplier partners, find information about being a HHI supplier.  SUPPLIER PORTAL »     


 CHINA CAREERS Find information about our career opportunities in China. CHINA CAREERS »      







ABOUT SPECTRUM HHI Hardware and Home Improvement (HHI) is a major manufacturer and supplier of residential locksets, residential builders’ hardware and faucets with a portfolio of renowned brands, including Kwikset®, Weiser®, Baldwin®, National Hardware®, Stanley®, FANAL®, Pfister™ and EZSET®. HHI is a leader in its key markets with #1 positions in U.S. residential locksets (Kwikset), Canada residential locksets (Weiser), U.S. luxury locksets (Baldwin), and U.S. builders’ hardware (Stanley-National Hardware), #2 in Mexico residential hardware (Fanal), and #3 in U.S. retail plumbing (Pfister).  Headquartered in Orange County, California, HHI has a global sales force and operates manufacturing and distribution facilities in the U.S., Canada, Mexico and Asia.
 
HHI is a division of Spectrum Brands Holdings, Inc. (NYSE: SPB).  Spectrum Brands is a global, diversified consumer products company and a leading supplier of consumer batteries, residential locksets, residential builders’ hardware and faucets, shaving and grooming products, personal care products, small household appliances, specialty pet supplies, lawn and garden and home pest control products, and personal insect repellents.  Spectrum Brands employs over 12,500 employees worldwide and sells to the top 25 global retailers with products in more than one million stores.  WHAT'S NEWView All News »  



